This paper is about large-batch training for deep neural networks, specifically for LSTM and CNN applications. The paper discusses techniques for improving large-batch training and achieving better results without losing accuracy. This topic is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE).
